    <etym xml:lang="ru">Из <ref type="xr" target="#entry_æ-"/> (негативная частица) + %idæwagæ%i, к
            <ref type="xr" target="#entry_idæwun"/> ‘отрицать’. Связь с <ref type="xr"
            target="#entry_daw"/> ‘обвинение’ и пр. менее вероятна.</etym>
    <etym xml:lang="en">From <ref type="xr" target="#entry_æ-"/> (negative particle) + %idæwagæ%i,
        to <ref type="xr" target="#entry_idæwun"/> ‘negate’. Association with <ref type="xr"
            target="#entry_daw"/> ‘accusation’ etc. is less probable.</etym>
